<SUBJECT>
<P>
GANGS -- ORANGE COUNTY; THREATS; ARRESTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020289-0163 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 13353 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 2, 1989, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
