COMMUNICATIONS; SELF IMPROVEMENT; SELF ESTEEM; JOB PROMOTIONS; EMPLOYMENT 
DISCRIMINATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020289-0185 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 13411 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 2, 1989, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
