Nowaczyk, left, soothes Jessie Vickery in quiet room. Jessie, feeling ill, had 
suffered bout of tears. Below, Sharon Coombs watches David Rodriguez take 
medication. ; Photo, Sherri Hayes supervises David Rodriguez and Jessie 
